# Loading Indicators

Loading and pending states must show a **spinner only**. Never render textual
status such as "Approving...", "Swapping...", "Processing...", or "Loading...".

Use the `Loader2` icon from `lucide-react` with `animate-spin` (size to context).

```tsx
// ❌ BAD - verbose status text (and branching on which action is pending)
{busy ? (
  <>
    <Loader2 className="size-4 animate-spin" />
    {isApproving ? 'Approving...' : 'Swapping...'}
  </>
) : (
  label
)}

// ❌ BAD - text-only pending state
{loading ? 'Processing...' : label}

// ✅ GOOD - spinner only
{busy ? <Loader2 className="size-4 animate-spin" /> : label}
```
